\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n用碌鳩打磨拍佢塊淫臉+奶 令佢成身都充滿住碌鳩嘅雄性味道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 用兩塊大臀肉同大淫奶玩臀交同夾腸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n狗仔式打屁股一邊打一邊問喺咪淫婦喺咪成日故意露奶誘惑人屌佢 再屌到佢叫老公 然後逼佢邊做愛邊打比老公 到襯傾緊個陣大大力打佢個大屁股<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n女下男上張腿當打椿機咁屌 最好屌一下啲淫水擠一大堆出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n從佢背後用手托開對淫腳令佢正面貼住窗咁屌 等鄰居睇下呢個大奶淫婦幾咁淫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中出之餘一定要射到佢成身都係精 再用有殘餘精液嘅大龜頭拍佢臉+磨嘴唇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後塞入口等佢舔乾淨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f6cb74722ebceef86f3921e101e9de354d32b41","tid":592484,"uid":140538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"82d5ac15a060225caa741a71f8e05cc88eae2eeb","tid":592484,"uid":31261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"07a8a57691ffaa7f25e22cb14a028bac5f0d5be7","tid":592484,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ca360ae040bf570150569bf005541178876f8eaf","tid":592484,"uid":140538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T12:48:51.000Z","msg":"係咪擺拍，同旁邊啲行家個style好唔同格格不入咁"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T14:43:03.000Z","msg":"正職唔係記者吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點會著對咁嘅斗零踭<br />\n唔洗追訪咩？<br />\n不過支那的確冇呢樣嘢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T14:52:08.000Z","msg":"對鞋7000幾蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 似花瓶多d"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T15:34:10.000Z","msg":"對鞋同個袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔怪之坳到隻腳咁對住鏡頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 中國人做雞特別多方法. jpg"}]}